description:
What is history if not memorizing facts and dates? #ANNInDepth host Sam Neves and ASTR’s Dr. David Trim discuss the meaning of history and it’s interpretation and understanding. This episode is for you if you like #AdventistHistory, Christian history, or history in general. 

Copy the link into your browser to watch the full episode: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YsyiooQITwg
